projector-game/
│
├── main.py                        # Main entry point
├── config/
│   └── settings.py               # Configs: camera ID, HSV range, homography points, etc.
│
├── detection/
│   ├── object_tracker.py         # Object (ball/pointer) detection logic
│   ├── hit_detector.py           # Logic for checking hits against hit zones
│   └── homography.py             # Handles camera↔projector coordinate transformation
│
├── game/
│   ├── hit_zones.py              # Defines and manages hit zones
│   ├── events.py                 # Hit triggers, score update, game logic
│   └── visualizer.py             # Overlay hit zones and debug visuals on frames
│
├── utils/
│   ├── smoothing.py              # Optional: smoothing for object tracking
│   ├── camera_selection.py             
│   └── timer.py                  # Debounce or delay logic
│
├── assets/                       # Store reference images, calibration photos, etc.
│
└── README.md                     # Project overview